About Us
The Anders family has a long history of welcoming sports fans, seniors, veterans, visitors and hardworking families to the End Zone Sports Grille. Our family and extended team work hard to create a friendly and sociable atmosphere, where customers and guests can sit down and enjoy a real hometown experience, with great food, good friends, and frosty drinks seven days a week.
You will enjoy watching your favorite sports teams play on one of our
50 flat-screen TVs
either inside our comfortably air-conditioned restaurant, or outside in our tiki for a real old Florida vibe. We subscribe to every premium sports channel, which covers the most popular college and professional games all year long.
Ask any one of our friendly bartenders and servers about our daily specials, catering, and game-day platters to go. They will take care of your drinking and dining needs with our reasonably priced American fare, that we create daily with only the freshest ingredients.
We offer one of the BEST Happy Hours in Englewood, offered daily from Noon to 6:00pm, with specially priced ice-cold Drafts and bottled Beers, Wine and Well-drinks.
When you are looking for a great night out where you can enjoy your favorite premium Beer, or specialty Cocktail, End Zone is the place to be, offering a wide selection of craft Ales, Lagers, top shelf Liquors, and Spirits – and some of the best LIVE Music and our famous Karaoke Night!
We are proud to consistently win awards in the yearly “Best of Englewood” contest for BEST Sports Bar, BEST Cheers Bar, BEST Place for Beer, BEST Chicken Wings and even BEST Philly Cheesesteak. We’re sure once you visit
End Zone Sports Grille
, you will experience our best, and enjoy making us your favorite sports bar in Englewood!
